We are proud to present a new version of our singing app: Now you can play a recording and seamlessly continue browsing the app. It makes using the app even more convenient. Double tap on the right side of a recording to quickly fast forward it by 10 seconds or double tap on the left side to rewind by 10 seconds. Clever That s what we thought! We have smashed some pesky bugs and optimised the app. We are constantly working on new features and are thrilled about upcoming changes. Thanks for singing on iSing! :

We are proud to present a big update. Here s what s new: Log in or create an account on iSing Record and publish your cover on your account Brand new navigation Browse popular and recommended recordings from iSing Subscribe other singers and browse your subscriptions If you already have iSing Plus on web you ll get access to Premium features in the app Bug fixes We are happy to present a major update to the app: Log in to your iSing account or register in the app Record yourself and publish covers on your profile New navigation Browse popular and recommended recordings Subscribe to other people and view new subscriptions If you have iSing Plus you will get access to the Premium option in the app Bug fixes
